bill.title: Combating Illicit Xylazine Act
bill.description: To prohibit certain uses of xylazine, and for other purposes.

history.action: Referred to the Committee on Energy and Commerce, and in addition to the Committee on the Judiciary, for a period to be subsequently determined by the Speaker, in each case for consideration of such provisions as fall within the jurisdiction of the committee concerned.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Health.
